name: oh god TOO FAST
description:
A little game about flying through space. You need CTRL JUICE to steer your ship but you're running low! Get as far as you can and watch out for black holes!

All assets were made in 2 days during the GMTK Game Jam 2020, where the theme was 'out of control'. In our game, control is a physical substance that you can run out of, which means you need to do some interesting maneuvers to survive.
